      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for anyone looking for reliable transportation on a budget. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading in the paint on the hood and roof. Inside, the cabin is functional but exhibits clear signs of wear, including some staining on the upholstery and minor cracking on the dashboard. Mechanically, the car starts and runs reliably, though it may soon require routine maintenance like new brake pads or tires. It\u2019s a solid, honest car for someone who prioritizes utility and value over cosmetic perfection.",
