    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition, representing a rare find for any serious collector or enthusiast. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, showroom-quality shine, and the body panels are perfectly aligned with no dents or scratches. Inside, the cabin is pristine, with leather upholstery that looks and smells brand new and all electronic features functioning perfectly. Mechanically, the car is impeccable, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history and no leaks or issues of any kind. You can expect a driving experience that is identical to when the car first rolled off the assembly line.",
