      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW\u2019s high-revving S54 inline-six engineering. Featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900-RPM redline, the powerplant delivers linear power through a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including proactive Double VANOS servicing and rear subframe reinforcement to maintain structural integrity under high torque loads. The factory limited-slip differential provides exceptional exit traction, while the chassis retains its signature balance and steering feedback. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its age, the mechanical components\u2014including the cooling system and suspension bushings\u2014are in robust condition, making this a turn-key driver's car for the purist.",
