    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 sports sedan in Mineral Grey Metallic. This vehicle has been kept in a climate-controlled garage and it shows; the paint retains a deep, glassy finish, though there are a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small 1-inch surface scratch near the rear wheel well that is only visible upon close inspection. The interior features premium Black Dakota leather that remains soft and supple. There is very light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster, but the passenger and rear seats appear nearly new. All cabin electronics, including the widescreen navigation, heated seats, and premium surround-sound system, are in perfect working order. Mechanically, the car is excellent. It has a complete service history with oil changes performed every 5,000 miles. Most recently, it received new brake pads and a fresh set of Continental all-season tires. The engine pulls strongly without any hesitation, and the transmission shifts are crisp and seamless. This is a solid, honest car that drives as well as it looks. Sale includes two key fobs, the original window sticker, and all service records.",
